data.description: **SELLER CREDIT OF 10K TOWARDS CLOSING COSTS/ INTEREST RATE BUY-DOWN**  Welcome to the home you've been looking for! Located in the HIGHLY sought-after community of SOUTH FORK in Riverview! Built in late 2021! This 2-story 4 bedroom 2.5 bathroom plus a flex/bonus room home is designed for COMFORTABLE family living. As you enter through the front door into the foyer, you'll find a spacious multipurpose flex/bonus room that can be easily used and transformed into anything you'd like. The open concept shared space among the family room, dining room, and kitchen is perfect for never missing out on quality family time together. With beautiful 42' inch espresso cabinets, granite counter tops, a kitchen pantry, and an oversized kitchen island you never have to worry about kitchen space again! Like new STAINLESS STEEL appliances and an entire home WATER SOFTENER and kitchen REVERSE OSMOSIS WATER FILTRATION system will be included. Continuing up to the second floor, you are greeted by a HUGE open loft space! The master retreat with a view overlooking the pond is a dream come true! Enjoy the spacious en-suite bathroom featuring a dual vanity sink, frameless glass enclosed stand up shower, and a private toilet room! Cluttered closets are a thing of the past! This master walk-in closet is a must see with endless space to never have to worry about running out of room again! Complimenting the master's retreat on the second floor are 3 additional very well proportioned sized bedrooms, an additional full bathroom, and a generously sized laundry room with washer and dryer included. With this home being located on an over-sized lot and a pond view you can experience FL LIVING at it's finest! Fire up the grill or get your smoker ready to enjoy the weather from the convenience of the 12x24 screened in lanai. The additional concrete pad makes it easy to cover and store your outdoor gadgets! South Fork amenities include swimming pools, walking trails, club house, a fitness center, basketball and tennis courts, playground, and more! Conveniently located near major highways, restaurants, shopping, and entertainment! DON'T MISS OUT! Contact me today to schedule you private showing!
